msgid "Device:"
msgstr "设备："

#: ui/main.qml:87
#, kde-format
msgid "General:"
msgstr "常规："

#: ui/main.qml:88
#, kde-format
msgid "Device enabled"
msgstr "设备已启用"

#: ui/main.qml:103
#, kde-format
msgid "Left-handed mode"
msgstr "左手模式"

#: ui/main.qml:118
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@option:check"
msgid "Press left and right buttons for middle-click"
msgstr "同时按左键和右键模拟中键点击"

#: ui/main.qml:130
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip from ContextualHelpButton"
msgid ""
"Activating this setting increases click latency by 50ms. The extra delay is "
"needed to correctly detect simultaneous left and right button presses."
msgstr ""
"激活此设置将增加点击延迟 50 毫秒。为了左键和右键的同时点击能被正确识别，额外"
"的延迟是必要的。"

#: ui/main.qml:142
#, kde-format
msgid "Pointer speed:"
msgstr "光标速度："

#: ui/main.qml:221
#, kde-format
msgid "Enable pointer acceleration"
msgstr "启用光标加速度"

#: ui/main.qml:235
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip from ContextualHelpButton"
msgid ""
"When enabled, pointer travel distance increases with faster movement speed."
msgstr "启用后，光标的移动距离会随着移动速度的加快而增加。"

#: ui/main.qml:245
#, kde-format
msgid "Scrolling speed:"
msgstr "滚动速度："

#: ui/main.qml:295
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Slower Scroll"
msgid "Slower"
msgstr "慢"

#: ui/main.qml:304
#, kde-format
msgctxt "Faster Scroll Speed"
msgid "Faster"
msgstr "快"

#: ui/main.qml:312
#, kde-format
msgid "Scrolling:"
msgstr "滚动："

#: ui/main.qml:313
#, kde-format
msgid "Invert scroll direction"
msgstr "反转滚动方向"

#: ui/main.qml:330
#, kde-format
msgid "Hold down middle button and move mouse to scroll"
msgstr "按住中键并移动鼠标以滚动"

#: ui/main.qml:342
#, kde-format
msgctxt "@info:tooltip from ContextualHelpButton"
msgid ""
"This will interfere with applications that use middle-button drag, such as "
"some image editors, document viewers, or video games. It may be used on any "
"device, but is intended primarily as a substitute for scroll wheels on "
"devices that do not have any."
msgstr ""
"这将干扰使用中键拖动的应用程序，例如某些图像编辑器、文档查看器或游戏。此功能"
"在任意设备上均可使用，但主要用于在没有滚轮设备上替代滚轮的功能。"
